# Golden stable — pinned by upstream Dify 1.13.3 itself in their docker-compose.yaml
# 0.5.4: null-content regression (#640) breaks agent tool calling + uv --offline (#649) breaks install
# 0.5.5: reverts uv --offline but STILL carries #640
# 0.5.6: broken auto-migrate (#672 removed migrate, CLI missing from image, #521)
# Unblock when upstream ships 0.5.7 fixing #640 and re-adding migrate

# --- ETL ---
# Docling 1.17 has RapidOcr regression: container ищет PP-OCRv4 ONNX model которая
# не вшита в образ и нет auto-download → startup FAIL. Stay на 1.16.1 пока upstream
# не починит OR не добавим pre-warm step (download models в volume до start).
DOCLING_IMAGE_CPU=ghcr.io/docling-project/docling-serve:v1.16.1
DOCLING_IMAGE_CUDA=quay.io/docling-project/docling-serve-cu130:v1.16.1

# --- AI Gateway ---
